<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MPB Branding | Demo Page</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --mpb-pink: #FF0081;
            --mpb-midnight: #020035;
            --mpb-white: #FFFFFF;
            --mpb-gray-light: #F2F2F2;
            --font-stack: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-stack);
            background-color: var(--mpb-white);
            color: var(--mpb-midnight);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 18px 5%;
            background: var(--mpb-white);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--mpb-gray-light);
        }

        .logo-svg {
            height: 24px;
            fill: var(--mpb-midnight);
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 32px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--mpb-midnight);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--mpb-pink);
        }

        .btn-sell {
            background-color: var(--mpb-pink);
            color: white !important;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            background-color: var(--mpb-midnight);
            color: var(--mpb-white);
            padding: 80px 5%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 500px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-text {
            flex: 1;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 64px;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.05;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            color: var(--mpb-pink);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            max-width: 480px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        /* Focus Ring Graphic */
        .focus-ring-visual {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .focus-ring-svg {
            width: 450px;
            height: 450px;
            stroke: var(--mpb-pink);
            stroke-width: 1.5;
            fill: none;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Content Sections */
        .grid-section {
            padding: 80px 5%;
            background: var(--mpb-white);
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--mpb-gray-light);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .card-link {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--mpb-pink);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        /* Footer Tagline */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--mpb-pink);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; padding-top: 40px; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 42px; }
            .focus-ring-svg { width: 300px; height: 300px; margin-top: 40px; }
            .nav-links { display: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">
            <svg class="logo-svg" viewBox="0 0 100 25">
                <text x="0" y="20" font-family="Inter" font-weight="900" font-size="22" letter-spacing="-1">MPB</text>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#">Buy</a>
            <a href="#">Sell</a>
            <a href="#">Trade</a>
            <a href="#">Explore</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn-sell">Sell your kit</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>The right way to <span>buy, sell and trade</span>.</h1>
            <p>The circular economy for creative gear. Smarter for you, better for the planet.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn-sell" style="padding: 16px 32px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none;">Get an instant quote</a>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-ring-visual">
            <svg class="focus-ring-svg" viewBox="0 0 200 200">
                <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" stroke-dasharray="2 4" />
                <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="95" />
                <line x1="80" y1="100" x2="120" y2="100" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.3"/>
                <line x1="100" y1="80" x2="100" y2="120" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.3"/>
                <path d="M40,40 L40,30 L50,30" />
                <path d="M150,40 L160,40 L160,50" />
                <path d="M40,160 L40,170 L50,170" />
                <path d="M150,170 L160,170 L160,160" />
            </svg>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="grid-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Change your kit, change your perspective.</h2>
        <div class="card-container">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Buy used gear</h3>
                <p>Every piece of kit is inspected and approved by our experts. Shop thousands of cameras and lenses.</p>
                <a href="#" class="card-link">Shop now <span>&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Sell your kit</h3>
                <p>Get a free instant quote and free insured pickup. Fast, secure payments direct to your bank.</p>
                <a href="#" class="card-link">Get a quote <span>&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Trade in</h3>
                <p>Upgrade your setup by trading in your old gear. The simplest way to change your setup.</p>
                <a href="#" class="card-link">Start a trade <span>&rarr;</span></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="tagline">Secondhandâ€™s got a new brand.</div>
    </footer>
